snippet.textDisplay: On one side, I don't think Morbius is interesting enough to have his own solo movie. On the other side, if this idea of giving villains their own movies so they could be introduced in the heroes movies later could make them more relatable and make audiences more invested on them; and people always said the most Marvel villains in the MCU lacked depth, so this could be a way to remedy it.
snippet.textOriginal: On one side, I don't think Morbius is interesting enough to have his own solo movie. On the other side, if this idea of giving villains their own movies so they could be introduced in the heroes movies later could make them more relatable and make audiences more invested on them; and people always said the most Marvel villains in the MCU lacked depth, so this could be a way to remedy it.
